Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa ta hanyar yanki kuma a halin yanzu, COVID-19 ya wuce sauran ƙasashe na duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon EU da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon mutane uku da aka tabbatar da su a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da ke dawowa daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK), tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kaɗai, tare da rahoton 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan kwanan wata.
