A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta ƙididdigar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito daga kowace ƙasa a duniya a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe, daga tushe na hukuma kawai kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da UK da kuma kwatanta su da cutar a Italiya.
