Mun kuma nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa da aka ruwaito a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da Italiya, a lokacin Janairu 31 - Maris 15, 2020.
