Wannan duk da cewa akwai matakai daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da ma'anar ma'anar shari'ar da za a iya bambanta a cikin ƙasashe, da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a bincika don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da kamawa da gwaji.
