Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) da ke haifar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000, kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, sakamakon hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar kwayar cutar SARS-CoV da ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa daga batutuwan kuma yana haifar da alamun kama da juna ta hanyar aiki iri ɗaya.
Ko da yake COVID-19 yana da ƙananan tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da yaduwa sosai kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
