Taron bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa tsammani ba ga duk mutanen China waɗanda aka nemi su zauna a gida a duk lokacin hutu da makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda barkewar cutar Novel Virus.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar SARS a 2003; saboda haka, a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya sunan SARS-CoV-2 kuma ta sanya sunan cutar da ke da alaƙa da cutar CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China kuma ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa duk ƙasar da kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 na duniya.
Har zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, an sami ƙarin lamura 80,000 da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 tare da fiye da marasa lafiya 40,000 da aka sallama daga asibiti kuma fiye da marasa lafiya 3,000 sun mutu saboda cutar.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine abokin gaba na 1 na jama'a kuma mai yiwuwa ya fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu bayan rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, an buga fiye da 200 articles akan COVID-19, ciki har da virology, epidemiology, forensics, diagnosis, da magani, wanda ya ƙaddamar da jerin ƙwayoyin cuta ta hanyar keɓewa daga marasa lafiya da yawa, a cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/).
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ya ba da labari game da ci gaban bincike a kan sabon kuma mai saurin bunkasa batun.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wasu cututtuka da ke haifar da CoV, kamar su cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya barke a shekarar 2012).
Za mu tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafi da kuma tsinkaya na cutar, da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci.
CoVs an yi imani da su a matsayin masu cutarwa ga mutane ba tare da cutar ba, da farko suna haifar da kusan 15% na mura na kowa 4.
Koyaya, a wannan karni mun fuskanci sau biyu na cutar ta mutum, wato, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka fara barkewa a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012 a bi da bi kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta CoV a cikin tarihin ɗan adam.
