A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an sami rahoton kamuwa da cuta a cikin masu ba da kiwon lafiya, wanda ya nuna cewa yiwuwar kamuwa da mutum daga mutum.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan tare da rufe dukkan hanyoyin zirga -zirgar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti kan cutar ya ba da rahoton cewa kawai 21 daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da ke da lamuran da aka tabbatar suna da hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan, wanda ake ganin shine farkon kamuwa da cuta daga wani tushen dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta ayyana annobar a matsayin bala'in kiwon lafiya na duniya.
A lokacin wannan rahoton, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk faɗin China da kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 na duniya (Figure (Figure 2).2).
Tun da yanayin yana ƙaruwa da sauri, har yanzu ba a ƙayyade ƙarshen yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar ba.
Nazarin da aka yi a wurare da yawa na marasa lafiya 8,866, ciki har da 4,021 da aka tabbatar da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020 ya ba da mafi kyawun hoto na annoba kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da mutane na kowane zamani, amma galibi tsakanin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne a ƙarƙashin shekaru 20, kuma mutane 14 ne kawai ke da shekaru 10 ko ƙasa da haka.
Maza sun fi kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 fiye da mata (0.27/100,000) da maza (0.31/100,000).
COVID-19 ya yadu a cikin garken da ke kewaye da Hubei.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farawa zuwa ganewa.
Matsakaicin lokacin incubation ya kasance kwanaki 4. 8 (3.0 - 7.2).
Matsakaicin lokaci daga farkon zuwa mutuwa ya kasance kwanaki 9.5 (4.8-13).
Lambar haifuwa ta asali (R0) ta kasance 3.77 (95% CI: 3. 51 - 4. 05) kuma daidaitaccen R0 ya kasance 2. 23 - 4. 82.
Yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai kafin 23 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya yi daidai da yawan zirga-zirgar ababen hawa a China kafin bikin bazara.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka tabbatar da su ya kai 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%) kuma adadi na mutuwar marasa lafiya ya kai 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Manyan abubuwan haɗari guda uku na COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥ 60), da kuma ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
CoVs wani ƙaramin iyali ne na ƙwayoyin cuta masu girma da kuma masu ɓoyewa waɗanda suke da ƙwayar RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya rarraba su zuwa tsara huɗu, wato, Alpha, Beta, Gamma da Delta, waɗanda aka san cewa Alpha da Beta-CoVs suna cutar da mutane.
Glycoprotein na shinge (S) yana haɗuwa da mai karɓar ƙwayarta na angiotensin - mai canza enzyme 2 (ACE2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), a cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, bi da bi, sannan kuma ya haɗu da membrane.
Kwayar RNA ta kwayar cutar ta fito cikin kwayoyin halitta; bayan kwayar cutar ta fito, kwayar halitta ta samar da kwayar RNA mai nau'in genomic tare da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid proteins, wanda daga baya ya hada da membrane na plasma don sakin kwayar cutar.
An sanar da jerin kwayoyin farko na SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
An gano SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin sabon nau'in beta-CoV wanda ya sami daidaiton kwayoyin halitta sama da kashi 99.98% a cikin samfuran jerin 10 da aka tattara daga kasuwar abincin teku ta Hunan, Wuhan, asalin asalin cutar.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kama da SARS-CoV a cikin kwayoyin halitta fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta hanyar watsawa ta hanyar duba siginar lantarki, an gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin sassan da ba su da kyau na kwayar halittar mutum.
An gano ACE2 na mutum, tare da SARS-CoV-2, a matsayin mai karɓa ga SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana haɗuwa da ACE2 na ɗan adam tare da rashin ƙarfi fiye da SARS-CoV wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani a cikin marasa lafiya fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya ƙirƙirar sabon ƙaramin furotin wanda aka tsara ta orf3b da kuma furotin da aka ɓoye wanda aka tsara ta orf8.
Orf3b na SARS-CoV-2 na iya taka rawa a cikin cutar kwayar cuta da kuma hana bayyanar IFNβ; kodayake orf8 ba shi da sanannen yanki ko yanayin aiki.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, et al. sun ba da rahoton tsarin cryo-EM na ACE2 na cikakken tsayi na mutum a ƙuduri 2.9 Å a cikin haɗuwa da mai ɗaukar amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa cakuda, wanda ke da kyauta da kuma rufewa, an tsara shi azaman dimer kuma ACE2-B0AT1 cakuda na iya haɗa sunadarai biyu na S wanda ke ba da shaidar ganowa da kamuwa da cutar CoV.
B0AT1, zai iya zama makasudin magani don gwajin magani don hana kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Abincin farko da na tsakiya
An san cewa SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV sun samo asali ne daga bat kuma an watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar civet cat da raƙumi, bi da bi.
Ta hanyar kwatanta jinsi na SARS-CoV-2 da sauran CoVs, an yi la'akari da bat a matsayin asalin mai gina jiki na SARS-CoV-2 saboda sabon kwayar cutar tana da kama da kashi 96% na SARS-like CoVs guda biyu da ake kira bat-SL-CoVZX45 da bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Koyaya, ba a san wane matsakaiciyar mai gina jiki ta taimaka wajen cutar da kwayar cutar ta ƙetare shingen jinsin zuwa ɗan adam ba kuma hanyar watsawa har yanzu tana bayyana.
Ji, et al., sun ba da shawarar cewa macizai sun zama masu ɗaukar kwayar cutar daga bat zuwa ɗan adam wanda ya haɗa da sake haɗuwa da S protein.
A cikin wani bincike, masu bincike a Guangzhou, China sun nuna cewa pangolin - mai tsayi mai tsayi, mai cin dabbobi masu shayarwa da ake amfani da shi a cikin maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin - na iya zama matsakaiciyar matsakaiciyar SARS-CoV-2 bisa ga kamannin kwayoyin halitta 99% da aka samu a cikin CoVs a pangolin.
Duk da haka, bambancin 1% a cikin dukkanin kwayoyin halittar biyu har yanzu babban bambanci ne; saboda haka, ana jiran sakamako mai mahimmanci don tabbatar da tabbaci (Figure (Figure 33).
Abubuwan jiki na SARS-CoV-2 ba a san su ba tukuna.
SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV na iya rayuwa na tsawon sa'o'i 48 a cikin yanayi mai bushe na wucin gadi da kuma kwanaki 5 a yanayin zafi da ke ƙasa da 20 °C da kuma 40-50% na zafi.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samun irin wannan halayen.
An bayar da rahoton cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da saukin kamuwa da UV a 56 °C na tsawon mintuna 30; ether, 75% ethanol, chlorine disinfectant, parasitic acid, chloroform da sauran mai narkewa na iya kashe kwayar cutar sosai, amma ba chlorhexidine ba.
Dukan al'ummar dan Adam ba su da kariya ga SARS-CoV-2 kuma saboda haka suna da saukin kamuwa da cutar.
Babu wani bincike mai zurfi da aka ruwaito game da amsawar rigakafi ga SARS-CoV-2.
Saboda haka, za mu iya yin nuni ne kawai ga binciken da aka yi a baya game da wasu CoVs, musamman SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV (Figure (Figure 4).4).
A yadda aka saba, bayan kamuwa da cuta ta shiga cikin mai gina jiki, tsarin rigakafin endogenous na mai gina jiki ne zai fara gane ta daga masu karɓar ganewar asali (PRR) ciki har da masu karɓar C-type lectin-like, masu karɓar Toll-like (TLR), NOD-like (NLR), da RIG-I-like (RLR).
Ta hanyoyi daban -daban, kwayar cutar tana haifar da bayyanar abubuwan ƙwayoyin cuta, balagawar ƙwayoyin dendritic da kuma hadawar nau'in I na interferons (IFNs) wanda ke iyakance yaduwar kwayar cutar da kuma hanzarta macrophage phagocytosis na kwayar cutar.
Koyaya, N protein na SARS-CoV na iya taimakawa kwayar cutar ta guje wa amsawar rigakafi.
Ba da daɗewa ba, tsarin rigakafi mai daidaitacce ya shiga cikin yaƙi da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Kwayoyin T, ciki har da CD4+ da CD8+ T sun taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen karewa.
CD4+ T cells suna motsa B cells su samar da ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman da kuma CD8+ T cells suna kashe kwayoyin cuta kai tsaye.
T ƙwayoyin taimako suna samar da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta masu hana kumburi don taimakawa ƙwayoyin karewa.
Koyaya, CoVs na iya hana T-cell aiki ta hanyar kashe T-cell.
Tsayayyar triphosphate, gami da ƙarin abubuwa da rigakafi kamar C3a da C5a, ma suna da mahimmanci don yaƙar kamuwa da kwayar cuta.
Alal misali, rigakafin da aka ware daga mai warkewa ya kashe MERS-CoV.
A wani ɓangare kuma, yawan amsawar jikin mutum yana haifar da yawan ƙwayoyin cuta da ke cikin jiki wanda zai iya sa a yi ciwo mai tsanani ga huhu da sauran gabobin jiki, har ma da rashin ƙarfi da mutuwa a cikin yanayi mafi muni.
Cutar SARS-CoV-2 mai alamar farawa a cikin garke na iya shafar tsofaffi da mata masu juna biyu.
Yana da kyau a lura cewa mutanen da suka kamu da ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa ko kuma waɗanda suke da tsarin rigakafi iri ɗaya suna iya kamuwa da cutar fiye da sauran.
Dangane da nazarin shari'o'i 425 na farko a Wuhan, an kiyasta matsakaicin lokacin incubation na SARS-CoV-2 kwanaki 1-14, mafi yawa kwanaki 3-7.
Duk da haka, nazarin shari 'yan 1,099 ya nuna cewa tsawon lokacin incubation ya kasance kwanaki 3 a matsakaici kuma ya kasance daga kwanaki 0 zuwa 24.
Kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, binciken kwanan nan bisa alƙaluma na 8,866 ya nuna cewa lokacin incubation ya kasance kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Daidaita lokacin keɓewa mai tasiri bisa ga mafi ƙarancin lokacin incubation kuma don haka hana mutane kamuwa da cutar amma marasa alamun cutar daga watsawa ga wasu mutane yana da mahimmanci ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
A matsayin al'ada, mutane da suka sadu da cutar ko kuma suka kamu da ita suna buƙatar keɓewa na kwanaki 14.
Shin ya kamata a ƙara tsawon lokacin keɓewa zuwa kwanaki 24?
Zazzabi shine babban bayyanar COVID-19 wanda ba shi da alamun bayyanar ko kuma yana iya haɗawa da wasu alamun kamar tari mai bushe, rashin numfashi, ciwon tsoka, dizziness, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, hanci, ciwon kirji, ciki, amai da kuma amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami wahalar numfashi da/ ko hypoxemia bayan mako guda bayan fara cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin yanayi, marasa lafiya sun sami ƙaruwa cikin sauri na ciwon ciwon numfashi mai tsanani, haɗarin haɗari, ƙarancin ƙwayar cuta, da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta.
Ya kamata a gwada marasa lafiya da zazzabi da / ko cututtukan numfashi da kuma marasa ciwon zazzabi mai tsanani, har ma ba tare da rashin daidaituwa na zane -zane na huhu ba, don gano cutar a kan lokaci.
Nazarin alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98 na alamun cutar zazzabi, kashi 76 na tari, kashi 55% na numfashi mai wuya, da kashi 3% na zawo; kashi 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon iska.
An ba da irin wannan sakamakon a cikin wasu nazarin da aka yi kwanan nan na garken da aka samu ta hanyar watsawa daga garken iyali da kuma mutum marar alamun.
A kwatankwacin haka, binciken alƙaluma na 2012 ya nuna cewa masu fama da cutar MERS-CoV suna da zazzabi (98%), tari mai bushe (47%) da kuma wahalar numfashi (55%).
Koyaya, fiye da marasa lafiya na COVID-19, kashi 80% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon iska kuma wannan ya dace da cutar MERS fiye da COVID-19.
An kuma lura da zawo (26%) da kuma ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya da cutar MERS.
