Waɗannan lambobin sun bambanta ta yanki da lokaci, kuma suna da tasiri ta yawan gwaji, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani, lokaci tun farkon ɓarkewar, da halaye na yawan jama'a kamar shekaru, jinsi, da lafiyar gaba ɗaya. Adadin mutuwa ya nuna adadin mutuwar da aka raba da adadin waɗanda aka gano a cikin takamaiman lokaci.
