Isra'ila ta nemi dukkan 'yan kasa su sanya abin rufe fuska a wuraren taruwar jama'a.
Taiwan, wacce ke samar da abin rufe fuska miliyan 10 a kowace rana tun tsakiyar Maris, ta sanya sanya abin rufe fuska a kan jiragen kasa da bas na tsakanin birane daga ranar 1 ga Afrilu.
Panama ta sanya sanya abin rufe fuska a waje, yayin da kuma shawarar yin abin rufe fuska a gida ga waɗanda ba za su iya sayan abin rufe fuska ba.
An kuma yi amfani da abin rufe fuska a Japan, Koriya ta Kudu, Malaysia da Singapore.
Yin nesa da jama'a (wanda kuma ake kira da nisantar jiki) ya ƙunshi ayyukan sarrafa kamuwa da cuta, wanda ke nufin rage yaduwar cutar ta hanyar rage kusanci tsakanin mutane.
Hanyoyin sun haɗa da keɓewa; ƙuntatawa kan tafiye - tafiye; da rufe makarantu, wuraren aiki, filayen wasa, gidajen kallo, ko cibiyoyin kasuwanci.
Mutane na iya aiwatar da hanyoyin nisantar jama'a ta hanyar zama a gida, ta hanyar iyakance tafiya, guje wa wuraren taruwa, amfani da gaisuwa ba tare da tuntuɓar mutum ba, da kuma nisantar da kansu daga wasu.
Gwamnatoci da yawa yanzu suna ba da shawarar ko kuma ba da shawarar nisantar zamantakewa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa.
An rage yawan jama'a da aka ba da shawarar ta hukumomin gwamnati na Amurka da kungiyoyin kiwon lafiya daga mutane 250 (idan babu sanannen yaduwar COVID-19 a wani yanki) zuwa mutane 50, sannan daga baya zuwa mutane 10.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, 2020, Jamus ta hana taron jama'a na mutane sama da biyu. Manya tsofaffi da mutanen da ke da yanayin rashin lafiya kamar su ciwon sukari, cututtukan zuciya, cututtukan numfashi, hawan jini, da kuma tsarin rigakafi masu rauni suna da haɗarin kamuwa da cututtuka masu tsanani da rikitarwa kuma CDC ta shawarce su da su zauna a gida kamar yadda ya yiwu a yankunan da ke da barkewar cutar. A ƙarshen Maris, 2020, WHO da sauran hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun fara maye gurbin amfani da kalmar "nesa" da "nesa ta jiki", don bayyana cewa manufar zamantakewa ita ce rage hulɗa ta jiki yayin kiyaye ko dai na kamala ko na nesa.
Amfani da kalmar "nesa da jama'a" ya haifar da ma'ana cewa, mutane su bi cikakkiyar keɓewa maimakon ƙarfafa su su ci gaba da hulɗa da wasu ta hanyar madadin. Wasu hukumomi sun ba da jagororin kiwon lafiya na jima'i don amfani yayin annobar.
Wannan ya haɗa da shawarwari na yin jima'i da mutumin da kake zama tare da shi kawai, wanda ba shi da cutar ko kuma alamun cutar.
An ba da shawarar keɓe kai a gida ga mutanen da aka gano suna da COVID-19 da waɗanda ake zargin suna da cutar.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ba da cikakkun umarni don keɓancewar kai. Gwamnatoci da yawa sun ba da shawarar ko kuma sun ba da shawarar keɓe kai ga dukan mutanen da ke zaune a yankunan da ke fama da cutar.
An ba da umarnin keɓe kai mafi ƙarfi ga rukunin haɗari.
Mutanen da suka iya kasancewa tare da wanda ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 da kuma waɗanda suka ziyarci ƙasa ko yanki kwanan nan tare da yaduwar yaduwar cutar an shawarce su da su keɓe kansu na tsawon kwanaki 14 daga lokacin da suka kasance cikin haɗari.
Dabaru na sarrafa ɓarkewar cutar su ne hanawa, da kuma ragewa.
Ana gudanar da rigakafi a farkon farkon barkewar cutar kuma yana nufin gano mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar tare da aiwatar da sauran matakan sarrafa kamuwa da cutar da allurar rigakafi don hana cutar yaduwa ga sauran jama'a.
Lokacin da ba zai yiwu a hana yaduwar cutar ba, ƙoƙari ya koma ga jinkirta: ana ɗaukar matakai don rage yaduwar cutar da rage tasirinta ga tsarin kiwon lafiya da al'umma.
Za a iya yin amfani da maganin hanawa da kuma maganin hanawa a lokaci guda.
Rashin ƙarfi yana buƙatar ƙarin matakan matsananci, don juya annoba ta hanyar rage ainihin yawan haihuwa zuwa 1. Wani ɓangare na gudanar da barkewar cutar mai yaduwa shine ƙoƙarin rage girman annoba, wanda aka sani da rage yanayin annoba.
Wannan yana rage haɗarin lalacewar kiwon lafiya kuma yana ba da ƙarin lokaci don haɓaka alluran rigakafi da magunguna.
Hanyoyin da ba na magani ba da za su iya sarrafa barkewar cutar sun haɗa da matakan rigakafin mutum, kamar tsabtace hannu, sanya abin rufe fuska da keɓewa; matakan al'umma da ake so don nisantar da jiki kamar rufe makarantu da soke taron taro; sa hannu cikin al'umma don ƙarfafa yarda da shiga cikin irin waɗannan hanyoyin; da kuma tsaftace farfajiyar kamar tsaftace muhalli. An yi aiki mai tsauri a cikin China don magance cutar lokacin da tsananin cutar ya bayyana, kamar ƙuntatawa da keɓewar birane da tsauraran ƙa'idodi.
Sauran ƙasashe ma sun ɗauki matakai da dama da nufin rage yaduwar cutar.
Koriya ta Kudu ta fara yin bincike mai yawa da keɓewa, kuma ta ba da gargadi kan motsin mutane masu kamuwa da cutar.
Singapore ta ba da tallafin kuɗi ga waɗanda suka kamu da cutar waɗanda suka keɓe kansu kuma suka sanya manyan tarar waɗanda suka kasa yin hakan.
Taiwan ta haɓaka samar da abin rufe fuska da kuma hukunta tara kayan kiwon lafiya. Yin kwaikwayon ga Burtaniya da Amurka ya nuna cewa akwai manyan ƙalubale a cikin ragewa (ragewa amma ba dakatar da yaduwar cutar) da hanawa (juyawa ci gaban cutar).
Daidai da hanyoyin magance cutar, za a iya rage bukatar kulawar lafiya ta musamman da kashi biyu cikin uku da kuma rage mace - mace da rabi, amma har ila yau, ana kashe daruruwan mutane kuma ana lalata tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Za a iya ba da fifiko ga hanawa, amma ana buƙatar kiyaye shi har sai cutar ta bazu cikin yawan mutane (ko har sai an sami allurar rigakafi, idan ta fara), in ba haka ba sassauƙa a cikin matakan yana dawo da watsawa cikin sauri.
Saurin tsauraran matakai don hana annobar yana haifar da tsadar zamantakewa da tattalin arziki.
Babu takamaiman maganin rigakafin cutar COVID-19 da aka amince da shi, amma ana ci gaba da kokarin ci gaba, gami da gwajin magungunan da ake da su.
Shan magungunan sanyi da ba a rubuta wa likitanci, shan ruwa, da kuma hutawa na iya taimakawa wajen rage alamun.
Dangane da tsananin, ana iya bukatar maganin oxygen, ruwan da ke cikin jijiya, da kuma taimakon numfashi.
Yin amfani da kwayoyin steroid zai iya sa sakamako ya yi muni.
Yawancin mahaɗan da aka riga aka amince da su don magance wasu cututtukan ƙwayar cuta ana bincika su don amfani da su a cikin maganin COVID-19.
WHO ta ce wasu "magungunan gargajiya da na gida" na iya taimakawa wajen rage alamun cutar SARS-CoV-19.
WHO ta bayyana haɓaka iyawa da daidaita kiwon lafiya don bukatun marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a matsayin matakin amsawa na farko.
ECDC da WHO na Ofishin Yankin Turai sun ba da jagororin don canja wurin albarkatu a matakai da yawa ga asibitoci da sabis na kula da lafiyar farko, gami da: mai da hankali kan sabis na dakin gwaje-gwaje kan gwajin COVID-19, soke hanyoyin zaɓe a duk lokacin da ya yiwu, warewa da keɓe marasa lafiya da ke kamuwa da COVID-19, da haɓaka ƙarfin kulawa ta musamman ta hanyar horar da ma'aikata da haɓaka adadin masu sanyaya iska da gadaje.
Akwai ra'ayoyi da yawa game da inda lamarin ya fara (wanda ake kira marasa lafiya).
An gano farkon sanannen yanayin cutar coronavirus a Wuhan, Hubei, China, a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019.
A cikin wata guda, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus a Hubei ya karu a hankali.
An fi yawan su ne a kasuwar cin abincin teku ta Hunan, inda ake sayar da rayayyun dabbobi, kuma ana ganin cewa cutar ta fito ne daga daya daga cikin irin wadannan dabbobi; ko kuma, a wasu kalmomi, ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi. An lura da wani nau'in cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san dalilin ba a ranar 26 ga Disamba kuma likita Zhang Jixian ne ya kula da shi a asibitin lardin Hubei, wanda ya sanar da CDC a Wuhan Jiangnan a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
A ranar 30 ga Disamba, wani rukuni na likitoci a asibitin Wuhan na tsakiya sun gargadi abokan aikinsu game da "kwayar cutar korona irin ta SARS".
'Yan sanda sun gargadi likitoci takwas, ciki har da Li Wenliang, kuma wani likita mai suna I Feng ya fuskanci tsautawa daga shugabanninsa, saboda yada jita -jita.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Wuhan ta ba da sanarwar jama'a a ranar 31 ga Disamba kuma ta sanar da WHO.
An sanar da hukumomin lafiya a Wuhan game da wasu cututtukan cutar sankarar bargo da ba a sani ba, wanda ya haifar da fara bincike a farkon watan Janairu.
A farkon da tsakiyar watan Janairun 2020, cutar ta bazu zuwa wasu lardunan Sin saboda yawan zirga-zirga da Wuhan, cibiyar sufuri da manyan hanyoyin jirgin ƙasa.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, China ta yi rahoton kusan sabbin mutane 140 a rana, ciki har da biyu a Beijing da mutum ɗaya a Shenzhen.
Bayanai na baya-bayan nan sun nuna cewa mutane 6,174 sun riga sun sami alamun cutar a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020. Har zuwa 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta zarce China da Italiya tare da yawan adadin waɗanda aka tabbatar da su a duniya. Har zuwa 9 ga Afrilu, 2020, an ba da rahoton fiye da mutane miliyan 1.61 a duniya; sama da mutane 97,000 sun mutu kuma sama da mutane 364,000 sun warke.
Akwai akalla mutum ɗaya a kusan ƙasashe da yankuna 200.
Saboda annobar a Turai, ƙasashe da yawa a yankin Schengen sun hana 'yanci tafiya kuma sun kafa matakan iyaka.
Amsoshin ƙasa sun haɗa da matakan hanawa kamar su keɓewa (wanda aka fi sani da umarnin zama a gida, umarnin mafaka a wurinka, ko kulle-kulle) da kuma dokar hana fita. Har zuwa 2 ga Afrilu, kusan mutane miliyan 300 ko kusan kashi 90% na yawan jama'a a Amurka suna cikin wani nau'i na kulle-kulle, sama da mutane miliyan 50 a Philippines, kusan mutane miliyan 59 a Afirka ta Kudu, da mutane biliyan 1.3 a Indiya.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, mutane biliyan 1.7 a duniya suna cikin wani nau'i na kulle-kulle, wanda ya karu zuwa biliyan 2.6 bayan kwana biyu - kusan kashi ɗaya bisa uku na yawan mutanen duniya.
An gano farkon tabbataccen shari'ar COVID-19 a Wuhan a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019; wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ya nuna cewa farkon lamarin ya faru ne a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba.
Likita Zhang Jixian ya lura da tarin cututtukan cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san dalilin su ba a ranar 26 ga Disamba, bayan haka asibitin ya sanar da Wuhan Jiangnan CDC a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
Gwajin kwayoyin farko na samfuran mai haƙuri a ranar 27 ga Disamba, 2019 ya nuna bayyanar SARS-like coronavirus.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Wuhan ta ba da sanarwar sanarwa.
An sanar da WHO a ranar.
Bayan wannan rahoton, 'yan sanda a Wuhan sun gargadi likitoci da su "yantar da jita -jita" game da barkewar cutar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin da farko ta yi ikirarin cewa babu "tabbacin tabbatacce" na kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ƙarshen watan Janairu, gwamnatin China ta fara wani mummunan yaƙi don hana yaduwar kwayar cutar, wanda Sakatare Janar na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin Xi Jinping ya kira "yaƙin mutane".
An bayyana shi a matsayin "mafi girman keɓewa a tarihin ɗan adam", an sanar da yankin kewaye don dakatar da motsi a Wuhan a ranar 23 ga Janairu, wanda aka faɗaɗa zuwa birane 15 a Hubei, wanda ya shafi mutane miliyan 57.
An hana amfani da motoci masu zaman kansu a cikin birni.
An soke bikin Sabuwar Shekara ta Sin (Janairu 25) a wurare da yawa.
Hukumomin sun kuma sanar da gina asibitin wucin gadi, asibitin Hoshensen, wanda aka kammala cikin kwanaki 10.
An gina wani asibiti, Lichenson Hospital, daga baya don kula da ƙarin marasa lafiya.
Baya ga sabbin asibitoci, kasar Sin ta kuma sauya wasu wurare 14 a Wuhan kamar cibiyoyin taro da filayen wasa zuwa asibitoci na wucin gadi. A ranar 26 ga Janairu, gwamnati ta kafa ƙarin matakan hana barkewar COVID-19, gami da bayar da sanarwar kiwon lafiya ga matafiya da kuma tsawaita hutun bikin bazara.
An kuma rufe jami'o'i da makarantu a ko'ina cikin ƙasar.
Yankunan Hong Kong da Macau sun kafa wasu matakai, musamman game da makarantu da jami'o'i.
An kafa hanyoyin aiki daga nesa a yankuna da yawa na kasar Sin.
An sanya takunkumin hana zirga - zirga a ciki da wajen Hubei.
An gyara hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a, kuma an rufe gidajen tarihi na ɗan lokaci a duk faɗin ƙasar Sin.
An kafa takunkumin hana zirga-zirgar jama'a a birane da yawa, kuma an kiyasta cewa mutane kusan miliyan 760 (fiye da rabin yawan jama'a) sun fuskanci wani nau'i na takunkumin fita waje. Bayan barkewar cutar ta kai ga matakin duniya a watan Maris, hukumomin kasar Sin sun dauki tsauraran matakai don hana "zuwan" cutar daga wasu ƙasashe.
Misali, Beijing ta sanya wa dukkan matafiya na duniya da ke shiga birnin wa'adin keɓewa na kwanaki 14. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an sami mutum daya ne kawai da aka kai gida a cikin kwanaki biyar da suka gabata a cikin babban yankin kasar Sin, a wannan yanayin ta hanyar wani matafiyi da ke dawowa daga Istanbul zuwa Guangzhou.
A ranar 24 ga Maris, 2020, Firayim Ministan China Li Keqiang ya sanar da cewa an dakatar da yaduwar cututtukan da ake yadawa a cikin gida kuma an sarrafa barkewar cutar a China.
An sassauta takunkumin tafiye -tafiye a Hubei ban da Wuhan a ranar, watanni biyu bayan an sanya dokar kulle. Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta sanar a ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020 cewa za a dakatar da shigar masu riƙe da biza ko izinin zama daga ranar 28 ga Maris, tare da ba da takamaiman bayani kan lokacin da wannan manufar za ta ƙare.
Waɗanda suke son shiga ƙasar Sin dole ne su nemi biza a ofishin jakadancin ƙasar Sin ko kuma ofishin jakadancin ƙasar.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta karfafa kasuwancin da masana'antu don sake buɗewa a ranar 30 ga Maris kuma ta ba da fakitin haɓaka tattalin arziki ga kasuwancin. Majalisar Jiha ta ayyana ranar makoki ta fara da minti uku na shiru na kasa a ranar 4 ga Afrilu, da karfe 10:00 na safe, daidai lokacin bikin Qingming, duk da cewa gwamnatin tarayya ta nemi iyalai su yi ta'aziyya ta yanar gizo, suna bin ka'idojin nisantar jiki don guje wa sabon barkewar COVID-19.
An tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 a Koriya ta Kudu daga China a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta ba da rahoton karuwar lamura da aka tabbatar a ranar 20 ga Fabrairu, wanda ya danganta da yawan jama'a a cikin wani sabon motsi na addini da ake kira Daigu, wanda aka sani da Ikilisiyar Shinchiji na Yesu.
Shinchiji Bhakti, wanda ya zo daga Wuhan zuwa Daigu, ya yi shakkar asalin cutar.
A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, 1,261 daga cikin mabiya cocin 9,336, ko kuma kusan kashi 13 cikin ɗari, sun ba da rahoton alamun. Koriya ta Kudu ta ba da sanarwar matakin gargaɗi mafi girma a ranar 23 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, an sami sama da mutane 2,000 da aka tabbatar da su a Koriya, wanda ya karu zuwa 3,150 a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu.
An killace dukkan sansanonin sojin Koriya ta Kudu bayan gwajin da aka yi ya tabbatar da cewa sojoji uku sun kamu da cutar.
Shirin da Koriya ta Kudu ta gabatar, wanda aka yi la'akari da shi a matsayin mafi girma kuma mafi kyawun tsari a duniya don bincika yawan jama'a don cutar da ke ware duk waɗanda ke da cutar, da kuma ganowa da keɓe waɗanda suka yi hulɗa da su.
Hanyoyin binciken sun hada da tilastawa kai tsaye na alamun cututtuka ta hanyar sabbin masu shigowa ta hanyar wayar salula, saurin gwaji don cutar tare da sakamakon da zai kasance a rana ta gaba, da kuma kara karfin gwaji don gwada mutane 20,000 a rana.
An yi la'akari da shirin Koriya ta Kudu a matsayin nasara wajen sarrafa barkewar cutar duk da cewa ba a keɓe dukan biranen ba.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardun neman a tuhumi Moon, ko kuma sun yaba da yadda gwamnatin ta amsa, suna zargin rashin kula da annobar.
A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa Koriya ta Kudu tana da mafi ƙarancin adadin masu cutar a cikin mako huɗu.
A ranar 29 ga Maris, an sanar da cewa za a keɓe duk sabbin masu shigowa daga kasashen waje na tsawon makonni biyu daga ranar 1 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 1 ga Afrilu, kamar yadda rahotanni ke nunawa, Koriya ta Kudu ta samu buƙatun tallafin gwajin cutar daga ƙasashe daban -daban 121.
Iran ta ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Komi, inda, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita, mutane biyu suka mutu a wannan ranar.
Matakan farko da gwamnati ta sanar sun hada da rufe kide kide da sauran al'adu, wasanni, da sallar Juma'a, da kuma jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi mafi girma da makarantu.
Iran ta ware tiriliyan biyar na Riyal don magance cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020 cewa babu wani shiri na keɓe yankunan da cutar ta shafa kuma za a keɓe mutane ne kawai.
An sanar da shirin rage zirga - zirgar tsakanin biranen a watan Maris, duk da cewa ana ci gaba da samun cunkoso tsakanin biranen kafin sabuwar shekara ta Farisa.
A ranar 16 ga Maris, 2020, wuraren ibada na Shia a Kom sun kasance a buɗe ga masu yawon shakatawa. A watan Fabrairu, Iran ta zama cibiyar watsa kwayar cutar bayan China.
A tsakanin ikirarin ɓoye girman cutar a Iran, sama da ƙasashe goma sun sami alaƙar shari'o'insu da Iran har zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, wanda ke nuna cewa cutar na iya zama mai tsanani fiye da shari'o'in 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito a wannan ranar.
An dakatar da majalisar dokokin Iran bayan da 23 daga cikin mambobinta 290 suka kamu da cutar a ranar 3 ga watan Maris.
A ranar 12 ga Maris, Human Rights Watch ta kuma bukaci hukumomin gidan yarin na Iran da su saki 'yan kare hakkin dan adam da aka tsare saboda zanga-zangar lumana ba tare da wani sharadi ba, da kuma sakin dukkan fursunoni masu cancanta na wucin gadi.
Ya ce, cibiyoyin da aka rufe kamar su cibiyoyin keɓewa suna da babban haɗarin yaduwar kwayar cutar, wanda kuma ya ƙunshi rashin isasshen kulawa ta likita.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, gwamnatin Iran ta ba da rahoton mutuwar mutane 100 a rana ɗaya, wanda shine mafi girma da aka samu a kasar tun lokacin da annobar ta barke.
Aƙalla 'yan siyasa da jami'an gwamnati 12 na yanzu ko na baya sun mutu daga cutar a ranar 17 ga Maris.
Har zuwa 23 ga Maris, ana samun sabbin mutane 50 a kowace awa a Iran kuma ana samun sabon mutuwa a kowane minti goma saboda cutar coronavirus.
A cewar wani jami'in WHO, adadin da ake samu a Iran zai iya ninka na yanzu da sau biyar.
An kuma ba da shawarar cewa takunkumin Amurka akan Iran na iya shafar ikon kuɗin ƙasar don amsa cutar.
Babban Kwamishinan 'Yancin Dan Adam na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya bukaci a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki ga kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa, ciki har da Iran.
An tabbatar da barkewar cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, lokacin da wasu 'yan yawon bude ido biyu na kasar Sin a Rome suka gwada tabbatacce ga SARS-CoV-2.
Lamarin ya fara ƙaruwa, wanda ya sa gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da duk jiragen da ke zuwa da dawowa daga China kuma ta ayyana dokar ta baci.
An gano wani rukunin marasa alaƙa na COVID-19 a Lombardy a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, farawa da 16 da aka tabbatar. A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, Majalisar Ministocin ta ba da sanarwar sabon doka-da-ka'ida don hana barkewar cutar, tare da keɓe mutane sama da 50,000 daga garuruwa 11 daban-daban a arewacin Italiya.
"A yankunan da ake fama da cutar, ba za a samar da shiga da fita ba", in ji Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte.
