A ranar 19 ga Maris, Italiya ta zarce China a cikin yawan mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da coronavirus a duniya bayan ta ba da rahoton mutuwar 3,405 daga cutar.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, an sanar da cewa Rasha ta tura jiragen soja tara zuwa Italiya dauke da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 5 ga Afrilu, Italiya tana da mutane 128,948 da aka tabbatar, 15,887 da suka mutu, da kuma 21,815 da suka warke, tare da mafi yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a yankin Lombardy.
Wani rahoto na CNN ya nuna cewa haɗuwa da yawan tsofaffi na Italiya da rashin iya gwajin waɗanda ke da cutar a lokacin na iya ba da gudummawa ga yawan mutuwar.
Amsar da Burtaniya ta bayar ga cutar ta bayyana a farkon farkon ƙasashe da aka shafa, kuma har zuwa 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta aiwatar da kowane nau'in nisantar zamantakewa ko matakan keɓewa a kan 'yan ƙasa ba.
A sakamakon haka, gwamnati ta fuskanci suka saboda rashin saurin da kuma tsananin amsawa ga damuwar da jama'a ke fuskanta. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya ba da shawarar dakatar da duk tafiye-tafiye da ba dole ba da kuma hulɗa da jama'a, yana ba da shawarar mutane su yi aiki daga gida a duk lokacin da zai yiwu kuma su guji wurare kamar mashaya, gidajen cin abinci da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za a rufe duk wuraren nishaɗi kamar mashaya da dakin motsa jiki da wuri-wuri, kuma ta yi alƙawarin biyan ma'aikata har zuwa 80% na albashin su har zuwa iyakar £2,500 a wata don hana rashin aikin yi a cikin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya sanar da matakan tsauraran matakan nisantar zamantakewar jama'a, wanda ya haramta tattara mutane sama da biyu da kuma iyakance tafiye-tafiye da ayyukan waje ga ayyukan da ake ganin dole ne.
Ba kamar yadda aka yi a dā ba, 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da wannan dokar ta wajen tara mutane da kuma tarwatsa su.
An ba da umarnin rufe yawancin kasuwancin, ban da waɗanda aka ɗauka "mahimmanci", waɗanda suka haɗa da manyan kantuna, kantunan magani, bankuna, shagunan kayan aiki, tashoshin mai da kaya da gidajen haya.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an tabbatar da sanannen shari'ar COVID-19 a cikin wani mutum a jihar Pacific Northwest na Washington, wanda ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu.
An kafa rundunar White House Coronavirus Task Force a ranar 29 ga Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya, kuma ta hana shigowar matafiya daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka - babbar cibiyar kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurka - ta sanar da cewa ta haɓaka kayan gwajin ta.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta fara gwajin a hankali, wanda ya sa ya yi wuya a fahimci ainihin yaduwar cutar a lokacin.
Gwajin ya kasance ta hanyar rashin ingantattun kayan gwajin da gwamnatin tarayya ta yi a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnatin tarayya ga kayan gwajin da ba na gwamnati ba (ta masana ilimi, kamfanoni da asibitoci) a ƙarshen Fabrairu, da kuma ƙuntatawa na ƙa'idodi (wanda ya buƙaci umarnin likita daga baya) don mutane su cancanci gwaji ɗaya a farkon Maris.
Har zuwa ranar 27 ga Fabrairu, jaridar The Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa an yi gwaji kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
Har zuwa 13 ga Maris, The Atlantic ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaji ƙasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, The Associated Press ta ba da rahoto: "Mutane da yawa da suke da alamun cutar kuma suna da umarnin likita sun jira na sa'o'i ko kwanaki don a gwada su". Bayan an ba da rahoton mutuwar farko a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu a Amurka, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ayyana dokar ta baci, wani mataki da wasu jihohi suka bi.
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke azuzuwan a ranar 3 ga Maris kuma a tsakiyar Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar suna rufewa. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, wani rukuni na masana ilimin cututtuka a Imperial College London ya shawarci Amurka game da hasashen tasirin sabon coronavirus a kasar.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Shirye-shiryen Cutar Coronavirus da Amsa, wanda ya ba da dala biliyan 8.3 a cikin kudaden gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya don mayar da martani ga barkewar cutar.
Kamfanoni sun hana ma'aikata tafiya, sun soke taro, kuma sun ƙarfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
An soke wasannin wasanni da zaman. A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya sanar da takunkumin hana tafiye -tafiye na kwanaki 30 ga yawancin Turai, ban da Burtaniya, wanda ya fara aiki a ranar 13 ga Maris.
Washegari, ya faɗaɗa takunkumin zuwa Ƙasar Ingila da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci ta kasa, wanda ya samar da kudaden tarayya don mayar da martani ga rikicin.
Farawa daga ranar 15 ga Maris, yawancin kamfanoni sun dakatar da aiki ko rage lokutan aiki a duk faɗin Amurka don ƙoƙarin rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga Maris, an tabbatar da annobar a duk jihohi 50 da Gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa New York City tana da shari'o'in 10,700 na coronavirus, fiye da jimlar shari'o'in da ke Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, Gwamnan ya ce nisantar zamantakewar jama'a yana aiki, saboda ƙididdigar ninkawar lamura ya ragu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
Har zuwa 28 ga Maris, New York City tana da lamura 32,308, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu daga kwayar cutar. A ranar 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta ba da rahoton ƙarin lamuran kamuwa da kwayar cutar coronavirus fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, gami da China da Italiya. Har zuwa 8 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta tabbatar da lamura 400,335 kuma mutane 12,841 sun mutu.
A ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaban Amurka Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idojin nisantar zamantakewar jama'a har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu, a cewar rahotanni na kafofin watsa labarai.
A wannan ranar, jirgin asibiti mai suna USNS Comfort, mai gado kusan 1,000, ya sauka a New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, an samu mutuwar mutane 884 a Amurka sakamakon cutar coronavirus a cikin awanni 24.
An soki fadar White House saboda rage girman barazanar da kuma umarci jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya da su daidaita maganganun jama'a da wallafe-wallafen da suka shafi cutar tare da ofishin Mataimakin Shugaban Kasa Mike Pence.
Trump ya nuna son kai wajen magance matsalar da ke da bambanci.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki dogaro da Amurka kan shigo da kayayyaki masu mahimmanci daga China, gami da kayan aikin likitanci masu mahimmanci.
An yi amfani da tsarin tafiye -tafiye na iska don yin bincike da kuma hasashen yaduwar kuma an buga shi a cikin tsakiyar Janairu 2020 a cikin Jaridar Tafiya ta Tafiya.
Bisa ga bayanan 2018 daga Kungiyar Jirgin Sama ta Duniya, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei sun sami mafi yawan fasinjoji daga Wuhan.
An kuma sanar da Dubai, Sydney da Melbourne a matsayin wuraren da mutane ke zuwa daga Wuhan.
An nuna Bali a matsayin mafi ƙarancin ƙarfi a cikin shahararrun biranen balaguro 20 dangane da shirye-shirye, yayin da biranen Ostiraliya suka kasance mafi ƙarfi. Ostiraliya ta fitar da shirin gaggawa na gaggawa don cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ya ce ba a san komai game da COVID-19 ba, kuma Australia za ta ba da fifiko kan kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin martani ga annobar.
A ranar 21 ga watan Maris, an ayyana dokar ta-baci ta lafiyar dan Adam a Australia.
Saboda ingantattun hanyoyin keɓewa na sufuri na jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da yawa suna shirin fitar da 'yan ƙasa da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, galibi ta hanyar jiragen da aka yi na ƙasar, wanda hukumomin China suka ba da izini.
Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus da Thailand su ne na farko da suka fara shirin kwashe 'yan kasarsu.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta fitar da 'yan kasar Sin ba.
A ranar 7 ga Fabrairu, Brazil ta kwashe 'yan Brazil 34 ko danginsu, ban da 'yan Poland huɗu, ɗan China ɗaya da ɗan ƙasar Indiya ɗaya.
'Yan ƙasar Poland, China, da Indiya sun sauka daga jirgin a ƙasar Poland, inda jirgin ƙasar Brazil ya tashi daga inda ya tsaya ya koma ƙasar Brazil.
An keɓe 'yan Brazil da suka je Wuhan a wani sansanin soja da ke kusa da Brasilia.
A wannan ranar, an kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (176 daga jirgin farko, da 39 daga jirgin na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi izini) daga Wuhan zuwa CFB Trenton kuma an killace su na tsawon makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama da ke dauke da 'yan Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a CFB Trenton.
Hukumomin Australiya sun kwashe mutane 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga Fabrairu zuwa Cibiyar Kula da Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sake gina shi a matsayin wurin keɓewa, inda suka zauna tsawon kwanaki 14.
Jirgin gudun hijira na New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu; fasinjojinsa (ciki har da wasu daga Australia da Pacific) an killace su a wani sansanin sojan ruwa a Whangaporoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawa da ke cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama da ke dauke da fasinjoji 129 na Kanada ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario, wanda aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasarta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga watan Maris, wani jirgin saman kamfanin South African Airways da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi hayar ya dawo da 'yan kasar Afrika ta Kudu 112.
An yi gwajin likita kafin tashi, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu waɗanda ke nuna alamun cutar coronavirus don rage haɗarin.
'Yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka gwada ba su da lafiya ne kawai aka mayar da su.
Sakamakon gwajin ya tabbatar da cewa duk 'yan Afirka ta Kudu ba su da cutar, ciki har da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin jin kai, waɗanda duk sun kasance a ƙarƙashin kulawa mai kyau kuma an keɓe su a wurin shakatawa na Ranch na tsawon kwanaki 14.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta ce kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da taimako ga China.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin daga jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen tura agaji zuwa sassan kasar Sin da cutar ta shafa, tare da wani hadin gwiwa a yankin Chicago da ke bayar da rahoton cewa sun tura abin rufe fuska 50,000 na N95 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Kungiyar agaji ta Direct Relief, a cikin hadin gwiwa tare da FedEx, ta aika da abin rufe fuska 200,000 tare da wasu kayan kariya na mutum, gami da safofin hannu da riguna, zuwa asibitin Wuhan Union ta hanyar jirgin gaggawa a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don kare "mutane masu hadari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya" tare da samar da kudade don binciken rigakafi da ƙoƙarin magani.
InterXon ta ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar masks 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, lokacin da Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da masks miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan a Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayan aikin likita sama da tan 13 a Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safofin hannu na likita miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin likita daban -daban, gami da kayan aikin 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da gudummawar kayan aikin likita tan 17.8 ga China da kuma alkawarin dala miliyan 100 a cikin ƙarin tallafi ga ƙasashen da abin ya shafa. Bayan da al'amuran suka daidaita a China, ƙasar tana tura taimako zuwa ƙasashe daban -daban waɗanda cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da kwararru zuwa Italiya don taimakawa wajen magance annobar cutar ta coronavirus.
Dan kasuwa Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kayan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don rarraba ta Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya, ya aika wa Panama kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000, da na'urorin motsa jiki 5.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Czech Republic sun nuna damuwarsu game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a China.
Misali, Spain ta dawo da kayan gwajin cutar coronavirus 58,000 da aka yi a China tare da daidaito na kashi 30 cikin dari, yayin da Netherlands ta dawo da abin rufe fuska na kasar Sin 600,000 wadanda suka kasance marasa inganci.
Belgium ta dawo da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da aka ɗauka cewa sun fito ne daga China, amma a zahiri daga Colombia.
A wani bangare kuma, tallafin da ake bayarwa daga China ya samu karbuwa a wasu sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da gaggawa na tallafi ga kasashe masu tasowa.
WHO ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi wajen sarrafa cutar da kuma shawo kanta.
WHO ta yi magana game da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin China da yin ɓoye-ɓoye wanda ya hana ƙoƙarin hanawa da sarrafawa, da kuma rikicin na yanzu inda gwamnatin tsakiya ta "ba da sabuntawa a kai a kai don kauce wa tsoro kafin hutun sabuwar shekara ta Lunar".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a mayar da martani ga shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na aiwatar da takunkumin hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Gallia ya yi sharhi cewa yayin da "ba a ba da shawarar WHO ba" wannan "lamari ne mai matukar muhimmanci na jajircewa don hana annobar a inda ta fi yawa" kuma ya kira shi "wanda ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum da kuma karuwar adadin sauran shari'o'i a wajen kasar Sin, WHO ta ayyana wannan annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a ta duniya (PHEIC), wanda shine na shida tun lokacin da aka fara daukar matakan rigakafin cutar a lokacin annobar cutar ta Flynn a shekarar 2009.
Daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC na haifar da "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye -tafiye, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili na matakan da ke tsoma baki ba dole ba a cikin tafiye -tafiye da kasuwancin duniya" kuma cewa "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar iyakance kasuwanci da motsi".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'umma ta duniya da ta ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don shirye-shiryen dabaru a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi, tana mai ambaton buƙatar taimaka wa ƙasashe waɗanda "ba su da tsarin da za su iya gano waɗanda ke kamuwa da cutar, koda kuwa ta fito".
Tedros ya sanar a cikin ƙarin maganganu, cewa "mu masu ƙarfi ne kawai kamar yadda muke da rauni" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su "saka hannun jari a yau ko kuma su biya ƙarin daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta gabatar da wani taron manema labarai a matsayin sunan da cutar ta COVID-19 ta kafa.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, António Guterres ya amince da ba da "ikon da dukan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ke da shi wajen mayar da martani".
Sakamakon haka ya haifar da kunna ƙungiyar gudanar da rikice-rikice ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya daidaita aikin na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda, a cewar WHO, zai ba su damar "mayar da hankali kan aikin kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya amfani da ƙwarewarsu wajen magance tasirin zamantakewar al'umma, tattalin arziki da ci gaba na barkewar cutar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kunna tawagar hadin gwiwar WHO tare da China don taimakawa wajen gudanar da gida da kuma ziyarar yankin don ba da gaskiya ga ƙwararrun ƙasashen duniya da na WHO a China, ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin ƙasa da kuma "tabbatar cutar da yaduwar cutar" da kuma kimanta "tasirin ayyukan mayar da martani a matakan lardi da na gunduma, gami da na birane da na karkara". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa "ya kamata duniya ta yi ƙoƙari sosai don shirya don yiwuwar cutar coronavirus", ta ce duk da cewa ya yi saurin faɗi, ƙasashe su kasance cikin "matakin shiri".
A cikin martani ga barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da tawagar hadin gwiwa don kimanta halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, hukumomin WHO sun ce za a kimanta barazanar coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "mai yawa", wanda shine mafi girman matakin faɗakarwa da kimanta haɗari.
A wata sanarwa, Mike Ryan, Darakta na Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta WHO, ya yi gargadin cewa, "Wannan gwaji ne na gaskiya ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: lokaci ya yi da za a farka.
Wannan kwayar cuta na iya zuwa kuma kuna buƙatar ku kasance cikin shiri", yana mai ba da shawara cewa matakan amsawa masu dacewa na iya taimakawa duniya ta guji "mafi munin sa".
