Gudanar da haɗarin yaduwar COVID-19 a wurin aiki
Aikin kiyaye lafiya da kiwon lafiya yana da aikace-aikace don sarrafa haɗarin yaduwar cutar COVID-19 a wurin aiki, don rigakafin cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kulawa mai kyau na haɗarin yaduwar cuta a wurin aiki ya dogara da wurin aiki da aikin da ake yi, wanda ya dogara da kimanta haɗarin tushen haɗari, tsananin cutar a cikin al'umma, da abubuwan haɗarin ma'aikata na mutum waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da COVID-19.
Aikin da ke da ƙananan haɗari na haɗari yana da ƙarancin haɗari na aiki tare da mutane da sauran abokan aiki, wanda ya haɗa da shawarar da aka ba da shawarar matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta, kamar: wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna rashin lafiya, bin ƙa'idodin numfashi, da tsabtace da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki a kai a kai, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Amurka (OSHA).
Ayyukan haɗarin haɗari na matsakaici sune waɗanda ke buƙatar yin hulɗa akai-akai ko kusa da waɗanda ba a san ko ana zargin cewa suna da COVID-19 ba, amma waɗanda na iya kamuwa da cutar saboda watsawar al'umma ko tafiya ta ƙasa.
Wannan ya haɗa da ma'aikata da ke da alaƙa da jama'a kamar makarantu, yanayin aiki mai yawan jama'a, da kuma wasu manyan tallace -tallace.
Baya ga matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta na asali, matakan kula da haɗari ga wannan rukunin sun haɗa da: yin amfani da matattarar iska mai inganci, amfani da masu kariya, da kuma samar da kayan kariya na mutum idan mutum mai cutar COVID-19 ya gamu da shi.
OSHA ta ɗauki ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da ma'aikatan gidan gawa suna da haɗarin haɗari waɗanda suka haɗu da mutumin da ke da cutar COVID-19 ko wanda ake zargi, kuma wannan haɗarin ya zama haɗarin haɗari idan ma'aikatan suka aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol, ko tattara ko sarrafa samfurori daga mutumin da ke da cutar COVID-19.
Kula da haɗari da suka dace da waɗannan ma'aikatan sun haɗa da kulawar injiniya kamar su ɗakunan watsawa na matsi da kayan kariya na sirri da suka dace da aiki.
Cutar COVID-19 na iya haifar da tasiri mai yawa a cikin wurin aiki.
Ma'aikata na iya yin rashin aiki saboda rashin lafiya, bukatar kula da wasu, ko kuma tsoron yiwuwar haɗuwa.
Yanayin kasuwanci zai iya canzawa dangane da waɗanne kayayyaki ake buƙata, da kuma hanyoyin samun waɗannan kayayyaki (kamar lokacin da ake buƙata ko sayayya ta hanyar isarwa ko sabis na motsi).
A ƙarshe, zirga-zirgar kayayyaki daga yankuna masu tasowa waɗanda COVID-19 ya shafa na iya shafar su. Shirye-shirye da kuma shirin mayar da martani ga cutar mai yaduwa za a iya amfani da su don jagorantar ayyukan kariya.
Shirye -shiryen suna magance matakan haɗari da ke tattare da wurare daban -daban na aiki da ayyukan aiki, gami da tushen haɗarin, abubuwan haɗari da ke haifar da gida da tsarin al'umma, da abubuwan haɗarin ma'aikata na mutum kamar tsufa ko yanayin rashin lafiya na yau da kullun.
Sun kuma bayyana matakan da ake bukata don magance hadarin da kuma shirin gaggawa ga yanayin da zai iya tasowa sakamakon barkewar cutar.
Shirye -shiryen da kuma shirye -shiryen amsawa ga cututtukan cututtuka na iya zama batun shawarwari na ƙasa ko na ƙasa.
Manufofin amsawa ga ɓarkewar sun haɗa da: rage watsawa tsakanin ma'aikata, kare mutanen da ke da haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin cututtukan kiwon lafiya, kiyaye ayyukan kasuwanci da rage tasirin tasirin su ga sauran raka'a a cikin sarkar wadata.
Matsayin cutar a cikin al'umma inda ake aiki yana shafar yadda ake amsawa.
Tsarin kula da haɗari tsari ne da aka yi amfani da shi sosai don tsara kula da haɗari bisa ga tasiri a cikin lafiyar sana'a da lafiya.
Inda ba za a iya kawar da barazanar COVID-19 ba, mafi ingantattun sarrafawa sune sarrafa injiniya, sannan sarrafawar gudanarwa, kuma a ƙarshe, na'urorin kariya na mutum.
Gudanar da injiniya ya ƙunshi ware ma'aikata daga haɗarin da ke tattare da aiki ba tare da la'akari da halayen ma'aikaci ba, kuma yana iya zama mafi kyawun mafita mai amfani a aiwatar.
Kulawa ta gwamnati canje -canje ne a cikin manufofin aiki ko hanyoyin da ke buƙatar aiki daga ma'aikaci ko mai aiki.
An yi la'akari da cewa kayan kariya na mutum (PPE) ba su da tasiri fiye da na injiniya da na gudanarwa, amma zai iya taimakawa wajen hana wasu hulɗa.
Dole ne a zaɓi kowane irin PPE ga ma'aikata bisa ga haɗarin, a sanya shi yadda ya kamata (misali, masu numfashi), a saka shi akai -akai kuma yadda ya kamata, a bincika shi akai -akai, a kula da shi kuma a canza shi kamar yadda ya cancanta, kuma a cire shi, a tsabtace shi kuma a adana shi ko a watsar da shi don guje wa gurɓata.
Aikin da ke da ƙananan haɗari na haɗari yana da ƙarancin haɗari na kasuwanci tare da mutane da sauran abokan aiki, in ji Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Aikin Amurka (OSHA).
Matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta na yau da kullun da aka ba da shawarar ga duk wuraren aiki sun haɗa da: wanke hannu da kyau da kuma sau da yawa, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna rashin lafiya, samar da ladabi na numfashi wanda ke rufe tari da sneezing, samar da kayan aiki da kwandon shara, shirya nesa ko layi daya idan ya cancanta, hana ma'aikata amfani da kayan aikin wasu, da tsabtace da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki akai -akai.
Ganowa da kuma warewar mutane masu cutarwa a wuri na aiki da wuri mataki ne mai mahimmanci don kare ma'aikata, abokan ciniki, baƙi da sauran mutane.
Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafi na Amurka (CDC) sun ba da shawarar cewa ma'aikata da ke da alamun cututtukan cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun su zauna a gida har sai sun sami damar zama marasa zazzabi, alamun zazzabi, ko wasu alamun cutar a cikin akalla awanni 24 ba tare da shan maganin rage zazzabi ko wasu magungunan canza alamun ba, kuma cewa akwai manufofin hutu masu sassauci waɗanda ke ba ma'aikata damar zama a gida don kula da dangin da ke da rashin lafiya, kuma cewa ma'aikata sun san waɗannan manufofin.
Bisa ga OSHA, ayyukan haɗarin haɗari na matsakaici sun haɗa da ayyukan da ke buƙatar maimaitawa ko kusanci tare da mutane a cikin ƙafa shida (1.8 m) waɗanda ba a san ko ana zargin cewa suna da COVID-19 ba, amma suna iya kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 saboda watsawar al'umma da ke kewaye da wurin kasuwanci, ko kuma saboda mutumin ya yi balaguron ƙasa da ƙasa kwanan nan zuwa wurin da ke da yaduwar COVID-19.
Waɗannan sun haɗa da ma'aikatan da ke hulɗa da jama'a kamar makarantu, yanayin aiki mai yawan jama'a, da wasu tsarin tallace-tallace masu yawa. Don wannan da kuma rukunin haɗarin haɗari, an tsara shirye-shiryen gaggawa a cikin sarrafawar injiniya, ƙara yawan hanyoyin sadarwa, kafa shinge na zahiri kamar masu tsaron filastik, da kuma kafa windows don sabis na abokin ciniki. Don wannan da kuma rukunin haɗarin mafi girma, gudanar da kulawar ma'aikata a cikin kulawar marasa lafiya a gida, canza tarurruka na fuska da fuska zuwa sadarwar kama-da-wane, kafa wuraren hulɗa na kama-da-wane, hana balaguron balaguro zuwa wuraren da ke fama da COVID-19, samar da shirye-shiryen gaggawa, gami da: samar da ma'aikata da ke da damuwa game da amfani da kayan aikin wanki na yau da kullun, samar da ma'aikata da ke buƙatar samun damar yin amfani da kayan aiki na yau da kullun, samar da horo ga ma'aikata da ke da ƙarancin haɗarin COVID-19, da kuma samar da kayan aiki na zamani, gami da takalma masu tsabta da kayan aiki masu kiyayewa, da kuma samar da horo ga ma'aikatan da ke buƙatar yin amfani da kayan aiki masu tsabta da kayan aiki masu kiyayewa, da kuma rage haɗarin COVID-19.
Ma'aikatan wannan rukunin haɗarin ba sa bukatar yin amfani da na'urar numfashi.
Idan mutum ya kamu da rashin lafiya a cikin jirgin sama, matakan da suka dace don kare lafiyar ma'aikata da sauran fasinjoji sun hada da: nisantar da mutum mai cutar da ƙafa 6 daga wasu, sanya wani memba na ma'aikatan da zai kula da mutumin da ke fama da rashin lafiya, da kuma ba wa mutumin da ke fama da rashin lafiya abin rufe fuska, ko kuma gaya wa mutumin da ke fama da rashin lafiya ya rufe bakinsa da hanci da nama idan ya yi tari ko sneezing.
Lokacin kula da matafiyi mara lafiya ko taɓa ruwan jiki ko ɓangarorin da ke da lahani, dole ne ma'aikatan jirgin su sa safofin hannu na likita, kuma idan matafiyi mara lafiya yana da zazzabi, yana ciwo, ko yana da wahalar numfashi, ya kamata a sa ƙarin kayan kariya na mutum.
Ya kamata a zubar da safofin hannu da sauran kayan more rayuwa a cikin jaka mai haɗari, kuma a tsabtace da kuma tsabtace wuraren da aka gurɓata daga baya. Don jiragen ruwa na kasuwanci, ciki har da jiragen ruwa da sauran jiragen ruwa, haɗarin yana cikin kula da dakatar da tafiya idan ya yi rashin lafiya da kuma keɓe kansa da kuma sanar da cibiyar kiwon lafiya a cikin jirgin nan da nan idan mutum ya sami zazzabi ko wasu alamun bayyanar yayin da yake cikin jirgin.
Ainihin, ya kamata a bi likita a cikin ɗakin da aka ware. Don makarantu da wuraren kula da yara, CDC tana ba da shawarar rufewa na ɗan lokaci don tsabtace ko kuma kashe ƙwayoyin cuta idan mutumin da ke da cutar ya kasance a cikin ginin makaranta wanda ba shi da hanyar watsawa.
Lokacin da akwai ƙaramin watsawa na al'umma, ana iya aiwatar da dabarun nisantar zamantakewa, kamar soke cin abinci a rangadin yanki, tarurruka da sauran manyan tarurruka kamar ilimin motsa jiki ko azuzuwan kiɗa ko gidajen abinci, ƙara tazarar tsakanin tebur, daidaita lokutan isowa da hutu, iyakance baƙi marasa mahimmanci, da amfani da keɓaɓɓiyar ofishin kiwon lafiya don yara masu alamun kamar mura.
Za a iya yin la'akari da tsawaita hutun makaranta, ban da dabarun nisantar zamantakewa, lokacin da akwai isasshen watsawa a cikin al'ummar cikin gida. Ga ma'aikatan tsaro da ke gudanar da ayyukan doka na yau da kullun, CDC ta ɗauki haɗarin lafiya na gaggawa a matsayin ƙasa.
Jami'an tsaro da ke da alaƙa da waɗanda aka tabbatar ko waɗanda ake zargi da COVID-19 ana ba da shawarar su bi ka'idodin da suka dace da masu fasahar likita na gaggawa, gami da kayan kariya na sirri.
Idan akwai kusanci yayin kamawa, dole ne ma'aikata su tsabtace da kuma kashe kayan aikin su da belin aikinsu, ta amfani da kayan aikin tsabtace gida ko gogewa, kafin a sake amfani da su, kuma su bi ƙa'idodin aiki don hanawa da kuma zubar da PPE da aka yi amfani da su da kuma hanawa da kuma wanke tufafi.
OSHA ta ɗauki wasu ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da na gawawwaki a matsayin waɗanda ke cikin manyan ko kuma manyan rukunin haɗarin haɗari.
Ayyukan haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da samar da kiwon lafiya, taimako, ma'aikatan dakin gwaje-gwaje da na jigilar likitoci waɗanda suka haɗu da waɗanda aka sani ko waɗanda ake zargi da COVID-19.
Waɗannan suna zama masu haɗarin haɗari sosai idan ma'aikata suka yi aiki, tattara ko sarrafa samfurori daga waɗanda ke haifar da aerosol akan waɗanda aka sani ko waɗanda ake zargi da COVID-19.
Hanyoyin da ke haifar da aerosol sun hada da tube penetration, cuff induction procedures, bronchoscopy, wasu hanyoyin da gwajin hakori, ko kuma tattara samfurin daga tsage.
Ayyukan gawawwakin da ke da haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da mutanen da ke shirya jikin mutanen da ke da sanannun ko kuma waɗanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwarsu; idan sun yi gwajin gawawwakin, za su zama masu haɗarin haɗari sosai. Ƙarin sarrafawar injiniya ga waɗannan rukunin haɗarin sun haɗa da ɗakunan keɓewa don sanannun ko marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19, ciki har da lokacin aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
A wasu wuraren kiwon lafiya da kuma gidajen gawa, ana iya yin amfani da takamaiman matsi mai guba.
Dole ne a kula da samfurori tare da matakan tsaro na 3.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa a ware marasa lafiya masu zuwa a yankuna daban-daban na jiran aiki, dangane da ko suna da cutar COVID-19. Baya ga sauran PPE, OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu numfashi ga mutanen da ke aiki a cikin ƙafa 6 na marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargin suna da cutar SARS-CoV-2, da waɗanda ke aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
A Amurka, NIOSH ta amince da N95 tace facepice respirators ko mafi kyau ya kamata a yi amfani da shi a cikin mahallin da m, rubutaccen tsarin kula da numfashi wanda ya hada da fit-testing, horo, da kuma likita.
Sauran nau'ikan masu numfashi na iya samar da ƙarin kariya da haɓaka kwanciyar hankali ga ma'aikata. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar rufewa ba, saboda COVID-19 cuta ce ta numfashi maimakon yaduwa ta ruwa na jiki.
WHO ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska guda ɗaya kawai ga ma'aikatan bincike a wuraren shiga.
Ga waɗanda ke tattara, kulawa ko jigilar samfuran numfashi daga marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da hanyoyin samar da aerosol ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar abin rufe fuska, tabarau, garkuwa da safofin hannu.
Idan an yi wani aikin samar da aerosol, ana maye gurbin abin rufe fuska da N95 ko FFP2 respirator.
Ganin cewa samar da PPE a duniya bai isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatar PPE ta hanyar telemedicine, shinge na zahiri kamar su buɗe windows, ba da izinin shiga cikin daki tare da mai haƙuri na COVID-19, kawai waɗanda ke cikin kulawa ta kai tsaye, amfani da PPE da ake buƙata don takamaiman aiki, amfani da na'urar numfashi ɗaya ba tare da cirewa ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali iri ɗaya, dubawa da daidaita sarkar samar da PPE, da kuma hana amfani da abin rufe fuska ga mutanen da ke da rashin lafiya.
