ACE2 sannan ya rushe carboxyl - terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp - Arg - Val - Tyr - Ile - His - Pro - Phe) kuma ya watse shi zuwa mai fadada jijiyoyin jini angiotensin (1 - 7), (H - Asp - Arg - Tyr - Ile - His - Pro - OH).
ACE2 [des-Arg9] na iya lalata wasu peptides da yawa, ciki har da bradycainin, epelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana sarrafa jigilar membrane na SLC6A19 mai ɗaukar amino acid kuma an nuna rawar da yake takawa a cikin cututtukan zuciya.
A matsayin furotin na parasite, yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na corona, ciki har da ACE2, HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
