COVID-19 Apps aikace-aikacen software ne na wayar hannu waɗanda aka kirkira don taimakawa wajen ganowa, wato, aiwatar da gano mutanen da ("saduwa") waɗanda wataƙila sun kasance tare da wanda ke da cutar, a cikin martani ga annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20.
An haɓaka ko kuma an ba da aikace-aikace da yawa tare da taimakon gwamnati a wasu yankuna da yankuna.
An tsara tsarin da yawa don gina aikace -aikacen ganowa.
An yi ta da damuwa game da sirrin, musamman game da tsarin da ke bisa bin diddigin yanayin yanayin masu amfani da manhajar.
Zaɓin da ba shi da hankali ya ƙunshi amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rajistar kusanci da sauran wayoyin salula na mai amfani.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar da cewa za su haɗa aikin kai tsaye zuwa tsarin aikin su na Android da iOS don tallafawa irin waɗannan aikace-aikacen da ke amfani da Bluetooth.
A China, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta tura wani manhaja tare da Alipay, wanda zai ba wa 'yan kasa damar duba ko sun yi hulɗa da mutanen da ke da COVID-19.
Ana amfani da shi a birane fiye da 200 na kasar Sin. A Singapore, ana amfani da wani app mai suna TraceTogether.
Aikace-aikacen da al'ummar IT na gida suka haɓaka, an saki shi a matsayin mai buɗewa kuma za a ba da shi ga gwamnati. Arewacin Macedonia ta ƙaddamar da "StopKorona!" aikace-aikacen da ke kan Bluetooth don gano alaƙa da mutanen da ke da cutar kuma samar da saurin amsawa ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
An haɓaka app ɗin ne ta Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya.
Har zuwa 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, wannan app yana jiran amincewa ta Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta ce manhajar ganowa tana cikin wani ci gaba na ci gaba, kuma za ta kasance a cikin makonni don tsarawa. An tsara irin wannan app ("StopCovid") a Ireland da Faransa.
Dukansu Ostiraliya da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen da suka dogara da TraceTogether na Singapore da kuma yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha tana son gabatar da aikace-aikacen geofencing ga marasa lafiya da aka gano COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow, wanda aka tsara don tabbatar da cewa ba sa fita daga gida.
Ross Anderson, Farfesa a fannin aikin tsaro a Jami'ar Cambridge ya lissafa wasu matsaloli masu yuwuwa na aiki tare da tsarin tushen app, gami da maganganun kuskure da yiwuwar rashin tasiri idan amfani da app ya iyakance ga ƙananan ɓangaren jama'a.
Da yake magance damuwa game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" masu yaudara ko cutarwa, Apple ya ƙayyade irin nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi da za su iya haɗa aikace-aikacen da suka shafi cutar coronavirus a cikin App Store, yana iyakance ga ƙungiyoyi "suna" ko kuma waɗanda aka yaba da su.
Google da Amazon sun kafa irin wannan takunkumi.
Masu fafutukar tsare sirri sun nuna damuwarsu game da tasirin sa ido mai yawa ta amfani da aikace-aikacen coronavirus, musamman ma game da ko za a lalata tsarin sa ido da aka gina don magance cutar ta coronavirus bayan wannan barazanar ta wuce.
Amnesty International da wasu kungiyoyi sama da 100 sun fitar da wata sanarwa da ke neman a takaita irin wannan sa ido.
Kungiyoyi sun bayyana sharudda takwas kan ayyukan gwamnati:
Dole ne sa ido ya zama "daidai, dole, da kuma daidaitacce";
Dole ne a sami sashe na ƙarshe don ƙarin kulawa da kulawa;
Amfani da bayanai ya zama iyakance ga dalilai na COVID-19.
Dole ne a kiyaye tsaro da kuma rashin sani na bayanai kuma a nuna cewa an kiyaye su bisa ga shaidar;
Ya kamata a guji sanya saɓani da kuma hana mutane samun 'yanci ta hanyar sa ido ta hanyar dijital;
Dole ne a ayyana kowane rabawa na bayanai tare da ɓangare na uku a cikin doka;
Dole ne a sami matakan kare haƙƙin 'yan ƙasa don magance cin zarafi da kuma amsawa ga cin zarafi;
Za a buƙaci "matsayi mai ma'ana" ta duk "masu ruwa da tsaki" ciki har da masana kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ƙungiyoyi marasa ƙarfi. The German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) da Reporters Without Borders (Reporters Without Borders) (RSF) suma sun fitar da jerin abubuwan bincike.
Manufar shirin Google / Apple da aka gabatar shine magance matsalar sa ido na yau da kullun ta hanyar cire tsarin ganowa daga tsarin aiki na na'urorin su lokacin da ba a buƙatarsa.
Wasu ƙasashe sun yi amfani da hanyar sadarwa maimakon aikace -aikacen, suna kawar da buƙatar saukar da aikace -aikace da ikon guje wa bin sawu.
A Isra'ila, an amince da bin hanyar sadarwa.
