A ƙarshen Fabrairu 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ce ba ta tsammanin samun allurar rigakafi a ƙasa da watanni 18 don kariya daga SARS-CoV-2, kwayar cutar da ke haifar da cutar.
