A watan Afrilu, an bayyana cewa, abubuwan da CEPI ke bukata don samar da allurar rigakafi su ne saurin, iyawar samarwa, tsarawa a kan sikelin da kuma samun damar duniya.
A watan Afrilu, masana kimiyya na CEPI sun sanar da cewa a farkon 2020 ana gudanar da bincike da ci gaban dandamali daban-daban guda 10 na fasaha don samar da ingantaccen rigakafi don kariya daga COVID-19.
Ƙarfafa manyan manufofin dandamali a cikin nazarin tsaro na Phase I sun haɗa da:
Kwayar nucleic acid (DNA da RNA) (mai haɓaka mataki na 1 da kuma ɗan takarar allurar rigakafi: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Mai ɗaukar hoto (mataki na I mai haɓaka da kuma ɗan takarar rigakafi: CanSino Biologics, Adenovirus Type 5 vector)
Kamar yadda masana kimiyyar CEPI suka sanar a watan Afrilu, akwai masu neman allurar rigakafi 115 a farkon matakin ci gaba, 78 daga cikinsu an tabbatar da su a matsayin ayyukan aiki (milken institute ya ce 79) da kuma wasu 37 da aka sanar, amma akwai karancin bayanan jama'a (wanda ake tsarawa ko kuma ake tunaninsa a cikin shiri).
